headline: Kimberly-Clark to Webcast its Presentation at Piper Sandler's Growth Frontiers Conference
summary: Mike Hsu, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Kimberly-Clark Corporation (NASDAQ: KMB), and Nelson Urdaneta, Chief Financial Officer, will be featured speakers at the Piper Sandler Growth Frontiers Conference on Wednesday, September 10, at 9:30 a.m. CT.

headline: Depend速 Teams Up with Ken Griffey Jr. & Sr. to Inspire Early Detection and Open Conversation Around Prostate Cancer
summary: Prostate cancer affects one in eight men1 and can lead to bladder leaks, yet remains a topic many still find hard to discuss. This Prostate Cancer Awareness Month, Depend速 is continuing its multi-year mission to break the stigma with sports icons Emmitt Smith and Ken Griffey Jr. & Sr. - raising awareness, sparking conversation and encouraging men to take charge of their health.
